query:
SELECT id, title, LEFT(content, 200) as content_preview 
FROM articles 
WHERE content LIKE '%numbered-teaser%' 
   OR content LIKE '%widget__%' 
   OR content LIKE '%border-radius%'
   OR content LIKE '%font-size:%'
   OR content LIKE '%display:flex%'
LIMIT 10;
